    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your affinity with the Shadow Plane allows you to draw a cloak of concealing gloom around you, even in bright light.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Stealth 9 ranks, shadow blending racial trait or shadow call shadowdancer prestige class feature.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>As a swift action, you can pull a haze of shadow around you, granting yourself concealment (20% miss chance) in bright light or normal light for 1 minute. You can use this ability once per day, plus one additional time per day when your character level reaches 12th, 15th, and 18th.",
